  <section id="registry" class="row">
    <div class="col-md-12 text-center">
      <h1>Registry</h1>
      <p>Your presence in our lives and at our wedding is our gift. We need nothing else. However, if you want to give us a present for our new home, we have set up the following [coming soon] registries. Thank you so much!</p>
      <div class="row">
